<template>
  <GChart
    :settings="{ packages: ['geochart'] }"
    type="GeoChart"
    :data="chartData"
    :options="chartOptions"
    ref="gChart"
  />
</template>
<script>
import { GChart } from "vue-google-charts";

export default {
  name: "geochart",
  components: {
    GChart,
  },
  data() {
    return {
      chartData: [
        ["Country", "Popularity"],
        ["SA", 3773870736],
        ["JO", 56090919],
        ["IL", 114142],
        ["AE", 60415],
        ["KW", 10874],

        ["IQ", 439],
      ],

      chartOptions: {
        region: "145",
width:900,        

        datalessRegionColor: "gray",
        colorAxis: {
          colors: ["#7ef9c0", "#088d4f"],
        },
        backgroundColor: "#799ed5",
        displayMode: "auto",
        // forceIFrame:true,
        keepAspectRatio: false,
        // enableRegionInteractivity:false,
      },
    };
  },
};
</script>
